    public class ViewerDialog
extends JDialog
implements ChangeListener
    A downsized version of the ArffViewer, displaying only one Instances-Object.
    版本:
    $Revision: 7904 $
    作者:
    FracPete (fracpete at waikato dot ac dot nz)
    另请参阅:
    ArffViewer, 序列化表格
